CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 13, 1966, pg. 11B, reads: "PANCA WINNERS IN NAACP MEMBERS DRIVE - Among the workers winning PANCA Awards in NAACP's 1966 membership drive were... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women, including Wilhelmina Byrd Brown standing in center, and men, including Rev. LeRoy Patrick standing in center of back row, and possibly Nate Smith on left, posed in interior with linoleum floor possibly for NAACP members drive
